name: Cube Master Fighter!
description:
Cube Master Fighter:

In this game you got to kill as many enemies as possible in the game. The more you kill the more points you will gain. If you do die, then you lose all your points. The enemies are zombies, and they spawn randomly in the game. Do you have what it takes to kill more than 100 enemies? Play this game to find out...

This game is still in development.

Game made by Jonathan Steadman. :)
